title: E3 is Cancelled - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.11.20
description:
E3 IS CANCELLED. Blessing and Gary are joined by Greg to discuss what E3's cancellation means for the industry.

Time Stamps - 
00:03:01 - Housekeeping
The Roper Report   -
00:04:26 - It's official: E3 2020 has been cancelled
00:21:27 - “Do you think we will still see a large number of announcements clustered together?” - Chase Winters
00:27:32 - “How will the cancellation of E3 affect industry insiders like yourselves?” - Krajookie
00:31:01 - “Who do you think strikes first as far as next gen announces are concerned?” - Probably Oliver
00:41:12 -  Ad
00:45:20 - It’s time for another Review Roundup: Nioh 2
00:51:51 - Doom Eternal is not true 4K on Google Stadia
00:59:03 - Two New Nintendo Directs Might be incoming
01:01:52 - Out today
01:03:46 - Squad Up: MarleyNito - PS4 - ingenito1993
01:06:11 - You‘re Wrong
01:10:58 - Post Show
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Greg & Blessing
